884. Sci Rep. 2018 Aug 22;8(1):12538. doi: 10.1038/s41598-018-30790-2.

A platform for discovery of functional cell-penetrating peptides for efficient 
multi-cargo intracellular delivery.

Hoffmann K(1)(2), Milech N(3)(4), Juraja SM(1)(2), Cunningham PT(1)(2), Stone 
SR(1)(2), Francis RW(1)(2), Anastasas M(1)(2), Hall CM(1)(2), Heinrich T(1)(2), 
Bogdawa HM(1)(2), Winslow S(1)(2), Scobie MN(1)(2), Dewhurst RE(1)(2), Florez 
L(1)(2), Ong F(1)(2), Kerfoot M(1)(2), Champain D(1)(2), Adams AM(5), Fletcher 
S(5)(6), Viola HM(7), Hool LC(7)(8), Connor T(1)(2), Longville BAC(1)(2), Tan 
YF(1)(2), Kroeger K(1)(2), Morath V(9), Weiss GA(10), Skerra A(9), Hopkins 
RM(1)(2), Watt PM(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Telethon Kids Institute, University of Western Australia, Subiaco, Western 
Australia, Australia.
(2)Phylogica Pty Ltd, Subiaco, Western Australia, Australia.
(3)Telethon Kids Institute, University of Western Australia, Subiaco, Western 
Australia, Australia. nadiam@phylogica.com.
(4)Phylogica Pty Ltd, Subiaco, Western Australia, Australia. 
nadiam@phylogica.com.
(5)Centre for Comparative Genomics, Murdoch University, Perth, WA, 6150, 
